  </div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="contact-section">
      <div class="contact-info">
        <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
        <p>Find us here: Located in the heart of the city, our office is easily accessible. Use the map below to find directions and get in touch. We welcome all visitors and look forward to connecting with you.</p>
        <div class="contact-details">
          <div class="detail">
